                            <h2 class="block-title"><span>End of the Year Information</span></h2>
<section class="html-wrapper"><div class="html-wrapper-inner" cms-block-content-root>
        <p class="tinymce-block">The following documents contain important information for students and their families about the end of the 2019-20 school year as a result of the mandatory school closures enacted due to the COVID-19 pandemic. Distance learning will continue as detailed in these documents. Everyone at the Thomaston-Upson School System continues to miss our students; and their safety, along with the safety of our employees and our greater community, remains a top priority. Please know that we are here to support you on this unprecedented learning journey that is the 2019-20 school year. Stay safe and stay well! We hope to see you all soon!  </p>
<p class="tinymce-block"><a href="https://resource.echalk.com/sr/YaeaHo90" target="_blank" title="FAQs" rel="noopener">Frequently Asked Questions</a></p>
<p class="tinymce-block"><a href="https://resource.echalk.com/sr/bUNwjomw" target="_blank" title="PK-8 Info" rel="noopener">Grades PK-8 Information</a></p>
<p class="tinymce-block"><a href="https://resource.echalk.com/sr/3PDYDjA0" target="_blank" title="9-12 Info" rel="noopener">Grades 9-12 Information</a></p>
    </div>
</section>
