            <div role="region" cms-block-id="6351980" aria-label="School Closures" class="content-block full html">
                            <h2 class="block-title"><span>School Closures</span></h2>
<section class="html-wrapper"><div class="html-wrapper-inner" cms-block-content-root>
        <p><span style="color: #ff0000;">In a press conference Wednesday, April 1, Governor Brian Kemp ordered the closing of all schools for in-person instruction through the end of the 2019-20 school year. Superintendent Dr. Larry Derico stated, “Based on this new information from the governor, TU school personnel will be working diligently to bring you important information about the remainder of the school year.” </span></p>
<p><a href="https://resource.echalk.com/sr/80ZWCaM9" target="_blank" title="April 13-17 Curriculum Packet" rel="noopener"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="caret-color: #ff0000;">April 13-17 Curriculum Packet</span></span></a></p>
    </div>
</section>
